n其實都係睇你想要咩 目標明確只係想RN過世 唔介意有冇degree同大學生活可以apply護校 快啲就可以出黎做野<br />\n好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實神科嘅原因唔關學科知識難度事架咩 照理dse 十零分應該讀唔掂個課程 仲要真係睇症"},{"pid":"0bfc9b2a4a1622fa9eaa63dc08d915610c3f8a66","tid":110113,"uid":13017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T12:51:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>登記護士同註冊護士既分別 好似係<br />\n利伸：唔多清楚</blockquote><br />\n護校係登記？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係有分RN同EN"},{"pid":"2e6628a3be4085b1e8e9c06222a2f6174481b81b","tid":110113,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T12:51:26.000Z","msg":"OU 都係RN<br />\n其實拎到牌既專業，比校名冇乜意思"},{"pid":"43e09d26771d2340b127caa7f54e47f1c1df295b","tid":110113,"uid":81234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T12:51:46.000Z","msg":"勁係RN威d？<br />\n利申外行人唔識"},{"pid":"d2f93959351ba5de7909b96954f408400cf021f1","tid":110113,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T12:53:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好奇問下<br />\n咁點解要咁努力考DSE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為U life會完全唔一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nOU 個校舍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ce1224048c6d6ee1e860cd152289b63ff95f9c2","tid":110113,"uid":13017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T12:55:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>OU有分EN RN<br />\nHA護校係RN但係冇degree<br />\n三大係RN <br />\n其實都係睇你想要咩 目標明確只係想RN過世 唔介意有冇degree同大學生活可以apply護校 快啲就可以出黎做野<br />\n好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實神科嘅原因唔關學科知識難度事架咩 照理dse 十零分應該讀唔掂個課程 仲要真係睇症</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n英文唔洗好勁 但一定要識識講<br />\n寫牌板啊睇報告好多都文件都英文 <br />\n遇著外藉嘅patient 你都要準確同人解釋返病情"},{"pid":"e7e21b45472c3adbcbbbfcda48e2a32704d0e43d","tid":110113,"uid":54516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T13:04:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>登記護士同註冊護士既分別 好似係<br />\n利伸：唔多清楚</blockquote><br />\n護校係登記？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係有分RN同EN</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n私家醫院開EN，HA先有EN及RN（非degree)課程。"},{"pid":"3786649b8c9a76d4a7cbe577e207d68869d0f57c","tid":110113,"uid":29780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T13:07:41.000Z","msg":"東華定明好好 如果一定要選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7776460b06ba81b1f107cc35b134e0b94414080e","tid":110113,"uid":29780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T13:08:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>東華定明好好 如果一定要選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n東華定明愛"},{"pid":"eee84e76b514222cdff757e3e6091089ba8a4b53","tid":110113,"uid":3581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T13:15:00.000Z","msg":"其他行業都係啦<br />\n<br />\n校名寄cv 個陣就有用<br />\n<br />\n之後無"},{"pid":"bc19fa7f46eef9f7926b6987fe7aeaf9629e7c16","tid":110113,"uid":42448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T13:17:57.000Z","msg":"登記護士可以等讀conversion course轉做註冊護士 不過有排等<br />\n而護士學校/高級文憑畢業嘅註冊護士出咗嚟做嘢可以part time補讀學位課程<br />\n之後同大學畢業嗰班無咩分別<br />\n可以一齊讀碩士 排隊讀專科 爭住升資深護師 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb0450cc12739a37c2db5c438e9965867019984b","tid":110113,"uid":53978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T13:23:59.000Z","msg":"個牌係一樣<br />\n但萬一真係唔想做呢行 <br />\n有三大degree轉行都易d啦"}]}